  "title": "AB03 - Wealth Advisor – Client Services",
  "description": "<p><strong>Wealth Manager</strong></p><p>Working Days: 5.5 Days (Mon – Fri: 9am-6pm; Sat is 9am till 1pm or depends to client appointment timing. <br />Working Location: Alexandra<br />Starting Salary: $2k - $5k (Depends on experience & qualifications)</p><p>Job Description:</p><ul><li>Understanding the needs of the customers (individual & company).</li><li>Analyse & tailor-made solution to meet their needs & concern.</li><li>Periodic Investment Portfolio / Insurance summary & review</li><li>Acquiring and servicing new and existing customers</li><li>Attend professional certification classes and courses.</li><li>Develop and implement financial strategies for individuals and small businesses.</li><li>Manage clients’ accounts and update them according to their life events.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Min Local Polytechnic Diploma.</li><li>Entry level is welcome.</li></ul><p><strong>If you are keen to apply, please send me your resume and job applied for on WhatsApp at 8093 8699 or email me at anabel.thesupreme@gmail.com (˶ᵔ ᵕ ᵔ˶)</strong></p><p>❄️Anabel Boon Xue Qi | Consultant Associate (R25159272) |📍The Supreme HR Advisory EA No: 14C7279</p>",
